<!-- Second (About) section -->
<section class="section" id="about">
    <div class="container">

        <h2 class="text-center title">About me</h2>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-sm-4 col-sm-offset-2">
                <h5><strong>About Me<br></strong></h5>
                <p>
                  My name is Kohl and I live in Saint Louis, MO. For the past few months I have been working at an experience design company called Manifest. We're on our way to becoming one of the biggest
                  Drupal shops in the country. Some of our clients include BMW, Allstate, Delta Faucet, CDW, Marriot, JCK, Brand USA, Post, and you can find even more <%= link_to 'here!', www.manifest.com %>.
                  Before building websites with PHP, I learned how to code in Ruby and Ruby on Rails. I am really interested in tackling iOS and MVC JavaScript frameworks next! When I'm not coding or working,
                  you might find me running in the park, playing guitar, exploring photography, or sharpening my improv skills.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-4">
                <h5>
                  <strong>
                    Career Goals<br>
                  </strong>
                </h5>
                <p>
                    I want something spectacular, that is mine, which I created from scratch. I love food; so much that for the longest time I thought about going to culinary school. In my wildest dreams, I see myself on the West Coast
                    at the beach, behind the grill of my beach bar, serving up homemade margaritas and fresh tacos filled with the local catch of the day. I'm a simple man with marvelous dreams.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

